<h2 id="defra-press-office-contacts">Defra press office contacts</h2>

<p>Journalists can contact the Defra press office through the following numbers:</p>

<h3 id="newsdesk">Newsdesk</h3>
<p>For media queries between 9am and 6pm on weekdays:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Telephone: 0330 041 6560</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="out-of-hours">Out of hours</h3>

<p>For media queries before 9am and after 6pm on weekdays, and on weekends and public holidays:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Telephone: 0345 051 8486</li>
</ul>

